reviewText: I would highly encourage anyone to but it on CD or on a different format rather than VHS. Most users don't have VCR's that can continue with this format for much longer. But these are funny, beyond witty, and just sick.

The whole video is a masterpiece! It's great! Each animation is very different, it takes you from laughing yourself to tears to feeling a great sorrow and under standing for a lone queen. A must have!
